ada was apprehended by members of the public and handed over to the Police last week for committing sodomy with a 10-year-old boy. May 30, 2014 In "News" A nine-year-old girl identified as Hassana Aliyu of Kasarau Yamma quarters in Dutse, Jigawa, has lost her life after falling into a well. February 1, 2019 In "News"